IN RE M.H. 2019-0621 Supreme Court of Ohio. July 10, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

Kennedy and DeWine, JJ., dissent.

APPEALS ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW

Appeal accepted on proposition of law Nos. I, II, and III.

O'Connor, C.J., would accept the appeal on proposition of law Nos. II and III only.

Donnelly and Stewart, JJ., would accept the appeal on all propositions of law.
